column3: yo yo yo  verse my mom sent me up to the store with a food stamp for a pack of cigarettes and a book at the newsstand here two dudes ran up jumped out of a blue van i looked down at the ground and picked up a huge branch i swung it at the first dude the other one with him seen it snap so fast it looked like it broke before it hit him so he tried to rush i swept his legs pinned him and bit him he came back with six or seven dudes screaming get him i grabbed one lit him on fire pinned and bit him the next faggot gave me his shoes like they didn't fit him one by one i just kept droppin' 'em in a rhythm then i woke up swingin' in the middle of the kitchen   damn damn damn
